HEADWORD: Petalosticha
<hw>Pet`a*los"ti*cha</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>PROP. n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL., from Gr. <grk>pe`talon</grk> a leaf + <grk>sti`chos</grk> a
row.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An order of Echini, including the
irregular sea urchins, as the spatangoids. See
<er>Spatangoid</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
